Class DocumentBuilderContainedEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.search.engine.spi.AbstractDocumentBuilder
      • org.hibernate.search.engine.spi.DocumentBuilderContainedEntity

  • public class DocumentBuilderContainedEntity
extends AbstractDocumentBuilder
    Set up and provide a manager for classes which are indexed via @IndexedEmbedded, but themselves do not contain the @Indexed annotation.
    Author:
    Gavin King, Emmanuel Bernard, Sylvain Vieujot, Richard Hallier, Hardy Ferentschik
